  criteriaText={"Trip estimates are per person from Tromso via Tromsø Airport (TOS), used as the busiest practical circumpolar-north gateway because the Arctic has no million-plus city. This page uses a practical gateway exception because the region has no resident million-plus city. The order is the ranking. Higher means rarer globally, more mind-expanding or harder to replace with a similar trip. Estimates assume economy flights where needed, midrange lodging, meals, local transfers, required fees and the shortest realistic visit."}
  tripOriginLabel={"From Tromso"}
